metadata.name: API
metadata.description:
API

Api means fire in Bahasa Indonesian. 

API’s eyes are the setting sun on a lake.

The crown is inspired by the handmade head adornments found in traditional Balinese dance, Akil Apollo Davis’  practice for 16 years. 

The leaves at the crown’s base invoke the alchemy of directed fire and the Sun.

API is envisioned by Akil, digitally illustrated in collaboration with Leia-lee Doran, and imbued with intention by the Animism Sekala collective.


API stands for:

Empowerment and motivation 

Balance and peace amidst energy

Cleansing

Vibrancy

Unflinching clarity

Mastery of power

Joy
